title: Christopher Nolan is a genius
content: I just finished watching "The Prestige." I thought I had watched all of Christopher Nolan's movies (besides "The Following" as I am saving it for when I'm older) but I guess I was wrong. I'm glad I was wrong. As always, Nolan's works don't dissapoint.

title: How many iterations of this website will I make???
content: I think this is my third iteration of this website. I have created an obsession.

title: Bass
content: I want to learn more about sound, specifically bass and how frequency changes penetrative capabilities through different mediums. Why? So I can blast music in my room without my sister telling me to turn my bass of.

title: Industrial Design
content: As I create this site I can't stop thinking about the design. I would seperate the design style into two: Industrial and Smooth. But I'm torn on which too choose.
